中示威入面所有違規警員<br />\n<br />\n2. 爭取全民直選立法、行政長官<br />\n取消功能組別 由下個立法會/行政長官選舉開始<br />\n<br />\n3. 特赦所有六月九至七月一所有示威者檢控</span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求其實有兩條都係冇意義<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301113\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301113</a>"},{"pid":"93a03466d304d837d309eb09ecb55d5820036960","tid":1301020,"uid":198553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:46:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"558272cee18e175b176ff58b514112a16a9b2035","tid":1301020,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:46:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af26265cb4de18dc70983b880a72f6c3f084349e","tid":1301020,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:47:51.000Z","msg":"貼警犬大頭"},{"pid":"c9d2a286e1dbb1a7930e081a11c2969dde2aa056","tid":1301020,"uid":155107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:48:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83915af52862c4c9b65835f85dfe91796eb626bd","tid":1301020,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"338354b28a61e6b2c99595a62dde5193798f35a3","tid":1301020,"uid":164442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/09/215438_d71acc073516a1924d1df549cec7ee21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F09%2F215438_d71acc073516a1924d1df549cec7ee21.jpg&h=6e23f9ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺FACEBOOK見到<br />\n<br />\n以下為貼文<br />\n<br />\n市民自發 光復上水<br />\n七月十三日 下午三點半<br />\n北區人 Assemble<br />\n<br />\n（路線容後發報）<br />\n<br />\n8/7/2019 update<br />\n<br />\n關注組知道大家關心是否有不反對通知書，明天關注組成員會跟警民關係科開會商討遊行路線及細節，之後要等警方那邊批出不反對書，我們亦希望警方可以盡早批出，讓大家可以安心地參與活動！<br />\n<br />\n我們重申一次，今次活動是市民自發，關注組的角色是協助申請不反對通知書及規劃遊行路線，我們相信市民是會以和平方式表達訴求，希望執法者不要帶有色眼鏡，用敵意去看待各參與市民，並希望你們在活動進行期間，將委任証配戴於當眼處，讓參與市民在你們的保護下，安全地參與活動，謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n再有新消息，將盡快向大家滙報，謝謝大家！<br />\n<br />\n#七一三光復上水 <br />\n#踢走水貨走私 <br />\n#還我寧靜上水<br />\n#香港加油<br />\n#不割蓆不分化不篤灰<br />\n#逆權運動<br />\n#18區大遊行<br />\n<br />\n轉至：北區水貨客關注組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2155059324617039&amp;id=253000284822962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2155059324617039%26id%3D253000284822962&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=b6d55833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2155059324617039&amp;id=253000284822962</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T00:36:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7e75fc5c73ba151d5ec3c2a836a27021d60db02c","tid":1301020,"uid":164442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:04:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87c7d1a91143b5bd0db8359b8d71db12d981e666","tid":1301020,"uid":76297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:11:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［推］7月行動行程整合！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ad75217db0c2e2adcbfed5ee0c544da52dee0ef8","tid":1301020,"uid":76297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:30:16.000Z","msg":"集合地點好似轉左！北區運動場籃球場"},{"pid":"4e25d0012ae17c669dcad1dcc8495e17fafe49cb","tid":1301020,"uid":164442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad75217db0c2e2adcbfed5ee0c544da52dee0ef8","tid":1301020,"uid":76297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:30:16.000Z","msg":"集合地點好似轉左！北區運動場籃球場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166351bcc0d8f1aa8535a715791848990b2999ca","tid":1301020,"uid":147643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b1